gomodel:SYNGO_5016  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 5: Electron micrographs of the stratum radiatum of the hippocampal CA1 region showing immunoparticles for Gβ5 (GNB5), as detected using a pre-embedding immunogold method. Synaptic localization was mostly to postsynapses with sparse labeling (5% of total particles) at presynaptic sites. Futher, extensive dendritic labeling was observed.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Six young adult (P30) OF-1 mice obtained from the Animal House Facility at the School of Medicine of the University of Castilla-La Mancha were used in immunohistochemical experiments at the light and electron microscopic level.\"\n\n\"Affinity-purified rabbit anti-Rgs7 and rabbit anti-Gβ5 were generated and characterized previously (Cao et al., 2008; Xie et al., 2012).\" PMID:21766168" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2023-02-18" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_5016" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

